TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION transformation performs a lookup on target table, DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT min(DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE) AS AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY AS CY_YEAR_YYYY, min(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_MONTH_NUM) AS CY_MONTH_NUM, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0') AS CY_WK_OF_YEAR, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0') AS FISCAL_YR_WK_ID FROM DAY_DIMENSION GROUP BY DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM = 'DR-DISC'
